article_id:1718,category_name:公告,title_name:关于《Dragalia Lost ～失落的龙约～》官方推特账号的推文【龙约新手TIPS】,image_path:,message:<div>《Dragalia Lost ～失落的龙约～》官方推特账号已发布面向新手玩家的推文【龙约新手TIPS】。</div><div>本公告将就【龙约新手TIPS】内容予以介绍。</div><div><br></div><hr><div>■长按篇</div><div>长按下方菜单的&ldquo;主页&rdquo;即可移动至上次挑战的任务！</div><div>长按下方菜单的&ldquo;圣城&rdquo;即可移动至建造或升级设施！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/0bf8e64a5674c2306d1f8669b46537c9.png"></div><div><br></div><div>■金币获得篇</div><div>装备可在商店交换所&ldquo;虚空之影讨伐战&rdquo;的&ldquo;特殊&rdquo;中交换的★5龙&ldquo;金法夫纳&rdquo;并挑战任务&ldquo;黄金之路&rdquo;可获得大量金币！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/318ad352660475fd9ccddc42c5c6ab95.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/2939ba6a85a7e7f11719be181b4b7e35.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■剧情跳过篇</div><div>使用主线剧情跳过功能可直接完成主线剧情第10章为止的任务并立即参与活动！</div><div>玩家Lv、设施Lv也将得到相应提升！还可获得强化素材等道具♪</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/782e96bc919d9c166f4839101f29a8e8.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■剧情跳过篇2</div><div>使用主线剧情跳过功能后也可随时回顾主线剧情。</div><div>可在连载中的&ldquo;纳姆的波澜冒险记！&rdquo;中以漫画的形式了解主线剧情♪</div><div><a href="https://comic.dragalialost.com/plotsynopsis/chs/">https://comic.dragalialost.com/plotsynopsis/chs/</a></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/3870d344a071138b953e92156f9365d5.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■敌人攻击篇</div><div>观察敌人攻击的红色标记配合时机发动技能可免受伤害。滑动屏幕进行回避动作时也可免受伤害。</div><div>需注意位于紫色标记的攻击范围内时无法规避伤害！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/76828d6df46deafd6d9eea7cb142463d.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/60b2147ff52f84c96039efe5a3db022a.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■队伍编成篇</div><div>装备与角色相同属性的龙和武器时可发动&ldquo;属性一致加成&rdquo;提升数值！</div><div>游戏初期难以凑齐相同属性，用现有的龙和武器编成自己的队伍吧！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/4d28fd8f27f8edd1b6c37eaccfd41e46.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/6e8722f1cf691e29099b1c0c1e48e32f.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■法夫纳币篇</div><div>收集法夫纳币通过商店交换所的&ldquo;法夫纳币交换&rdquo;获得稀有素材吧！</div><div>也可交换&ldquo;龙之庭院Ver.&rdquo;的龙！其拥有不限属性的能力，非常适合新手！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/51f51c94adb23e957b4d1922806e7549.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/ae367b98b0c2996949998ab07b803571.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■点击素材篇</div><div>武器制造&amp;强化和建造页面中点击所需道具图标即可显示可获得该道具的任务！</div><div>如道具可在交换所获得，还可直接交换！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/c1b1135da30bb9da034133b0c2da109b.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/fa4164ada88f1e986831ea7686e1305a.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/785a82981b44e04430bfcd35bb4ba57b.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/1cfdf47c92b686296fe43cb6da2f8ab8.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■日常目标篇</div><div>完成&ldquo;日常目标&rdquo;即可获得道具。</div><div>完成所有&ldquo;日常目标&rdquo;还可获得50个龙辉晶！</div><div>记得每天都进行挑战哦！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/68fb2b59a64c16fbfd19c7b1a8a2192e.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■王子育成训练篇</div><div>完成&ldquo;王子育成训练&rdquo;的作业即可获得强化素材和召唤券等道具！</div><div>争取全部完成吧♪</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/b799074dde99c41d79d74d2e210bff6d.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/bc70c22c981dfa9e23b290810cdbb0e7.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■任务篇</div><div>任务挑战失败时将不消耗体力和共斗之翼。</div><div>大胆进行挑战吧！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/ff7448cdbc62d9b1b5c8bf3ac1bf34f6.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/907e3dec2579b492debe136fa7e8d2a1.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■龙辉护符篇</div><div>龙辉护符可通过任务和商店的&ldquo;龙辉护符交换所&rdquo;等途径获得！</div><div>不知选哪个好时推荐选择可提升技能伤害或可发动联阵加成的护符哦♪</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/9114324c2807d63f34711a48d2d2fd86.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/c07b1656cf12a5ac121bdeea3e7bebbe.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/e729dd640c6b8aa4af2dfb8e95c0189b.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/54fa189d4685476273a7b44c54c194ed.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■商店篇</div><div>商店的&ldquo;育成道具 育成礼包&rdquo;中每天均可免费进行1次&ldquo;道具召唤&rdquo;，也可用金币购买育成道具！</div><div>别忘了每天进行道具召唤哦！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/101ee941864316e27d80199294b13ca5.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/c3ac62aaa40dcd8f6d67181372289f6b.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/d6d962ebe47e95b35f35bb3d72bc440b.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■交换所篇</div><div>可在商店的交换所中交换各种道具和设施！</div><div>其中更有非常稀有的道具♪</div><div>设施对于战力的提升不可或缺，一定要交换哦！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/9d8740325af1848ddea6536a51f9775d.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/aed3cc4e97da62cbc977cf5aee733644.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/e8bb3939e6fca82ae3afdfe733ffc987.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/08355402b8403ad566bd95481d8a90ba.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■强化素材获得篇</div><div>可在任务&ldquo;成长之路&rdquo;中获得用于强化角色、龙和武器的经验值素材道具！</div><div>用于强化龙辉护符的道具则可在活动中获得！</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/0c795b2c464a7df705d42c9902ca2b2f.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/757efd13dc5d373e61bb16f036ad776a.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><div>■回忆活动篇</div><div>参与&ldquo;回忆活动&rdquo;体验过去开放的部分设施活动有助于提升圣城的合计设施Lv！</div><div>可随时切换活动，踊跃参与吧♪</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/9ced91848b4081e714a2d9a05a70bc88.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/a2ecdbaebf267a776bda1c410fe1c7c3.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/ec0c1a309a74775c29f36719d057b1a8.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/f3b93c3f1b04185fb73f5961206748dd.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div>■反复攻略功能篇</div><div>已完成所有任务目标的任务可通过&ldquo;反复攻略功能&rdquo;自动进行反复攻略！</div><div>降低刷图负担，轻松收集素材♪</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/8f2388433945b74c929fd0f14fbb4ed9.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/40b17dac376d3575e26cfe950e9c8697.png" style="width: 289px; height: 500px;"></div><div><br></div><hr><div>希望能为各位新手玩家带来帮助。</div><div>同时也感谢各位老玩家的众多回复！</div><div><a href="https://twitter.com/dragalialost/status/1312649667570626567">期待能有更多能帮到新手玩家的TIPS！</a></div><div><br></div><div>今后也请继续支持《Dragalia Lost ～失落的龙约～》。</div>,start_time:1603260000,update_time1603259408